          <p class="text-body text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
            A single strategy is brittle. Markets are regime-dependent: what works in trending days fails on mean-reversion days. DeltaForge runs <strong class="text-foreground">five strategies in parallel</strong>, each generating a signal with a confidence score. The engine picks the highest-confidence signal above threshold.
          </p>

