          <p class="text-body text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The key distinction: <strong class="text-foreground">Reject</strong> means the signal is skipped but trading continues. <strong class="text-foreground">HALT</strong> means the system stops for the entire session. Gates 1-5 trigger halts because they indicate something structurally wrong: you're losing too much money and need to stop.
