          <p class="text-body text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
            An autonomous trading system without a kill switch is a ticking bomb. DeltaForge's kill switch is an <strong class="text-foreground">independent watchdog process</strong>, completely separate from the main trading engine. If the engine hangs, crashes, or enters an infinite loop, the kill switch still works.
          </p>

